synopsis: In town for a job interview, a young woman arrives at her Airbnb late at night only to find that it has been mistakenly double-booked and a strange man is already staying there. Against her better judgement, she decides to stay the night anyway, but soon discovers that there is much more to be afraid of in the house than the other guest.
tagline: Some stay for a night. Some stay for a week. Some never leave.
casting: ['Georgina Campbell', 'Bill Skarsgård', 'Justin Long', 'Matthew Patrick Davis', 'Richard Brake', 'Kurt Braunohler', 'Jaymes Butler', 'Sophie Sörensen', 'Rachel Fowler', 'J.R. synopsis: A documentary about dolphins that cover the recent story of a Japanese massacre of dolphins as well as other footage of swimming with dolphins.
A paranoid recluse is drawn into a sinister rabbit hole of conspiracy when he begins to suspect that something is watching……
tagline: madness of the mind is one of a kind
